---
const FORM_ACTION = 'https://news.reichenberg.ruhr/subscription/form';
const LIST_UUID = '888324d2-1852-4e46-b06d-7e6f4e2c3f9c';
---

<section class="section" id="newsletter" data-id="#05 / newsletter">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">05 — Newsletter</span>
    <h2 class="nl-headline">Täglich die viralsten <em>KI-News</em> im Postfach</h2>
    <p class="nl-sub">
      Jeden Morgen kuratiert: neue Modelle, Tools &amp; Repos, Agenten &amp; MCP,
      Self-Hosting &amp; RAG — auf Deutsch, ohne Füllmaterial. Abmeldung jederzeit
      mit einem Klick.
    </p>

    <form class="nl-form" action={FORM_ACTION} method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="nonce" />
      <input type="hidden" name="l" value={LIST_UUID} />
      <span class="nl-ps1" aria-hidden="true">subscribe --email</span>
      <input
        class="nl-input"
        type="email"
        name="email"
        required
        placeholder="du@beispiel.de"
        aria-label="E-Mail-Adresse"
      />
      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">abonnieren</button>
    </form>

    <p class="nl-note">
      Double-Opt-in: Du bekommst zuerst eine Bestätigungsmail. Abmeldung jederzeit über den
      Link in jeder Ausgabe. Details in der <a href="/datenschutz">Datenschutzerklärung</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .nl-headline {
    font-size: var(--h2-size);
    font-weight: var(--h2-weight);
    letter-spacing: var(--h2-tracking);
    margin-top: 18px;
  }
  .nl-headline em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
  .nl-sub {
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .nl-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .nl-ps1 {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 13px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .nl-input {
    font: inherit;
    flex: 1 1 200px;
    min-width: 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }
  .nl-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .nl-input:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .nl-note {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .nl-note a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: underline; }
  .nl-note a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
</style>
